    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "Anyways, my shift is near ending. So maybe we could hang out to some cool place after."
            ],
            [
                "Make yourself comfortable in the meantime."
            ],
            [
                "Well, I would... but... I remember someone promised me a free coffee on the speed dating event yesterday."
            ],
            [
                "Wait, really? Who is it?"
            ],
            [
                "You are dating a barista? Who are they?"
            ],
            [
                "..."
            ],
            [
                "Oh--- dumb... it was me."
            ],
            [
                "Sure, I'll make you some coffee."
            ],
            [
                "What is gonna be? Oh wait... nevermind, I've seen many faces around here."
            ],
            [
                "I know what kind of coffe you'd like from the face alone."
            ],
            [
                "Hold tight, [tn]"
            ],
            [
                "I sit in one of the tables...."
            ],
            [
                "Minutes pass"
            ],
            [
                "Maybe half an hour already."
            ],
            [
                "Hey I'm out already. Shift's over"
            ],
            [
                "I thought you were..."
            ],
            [
                "Tah-Dah!"
            ],
            [
                "Victor pulled out a coffee cup from behind"
            ],
            [
                "Weren't gonna forget that!"
            ],
            [
                "Go on, tell me if I got it right."
            ],
            [
                "In the meantime we could walk to the park"
            ],
            [
                "We walk along the busy streets until reaching the park"
            ],
            [
                "So how's the coffee?"
            ],
            [
                "I'd say it's pretty good."
            ],
            [
                "How did you got it right?"
            ],
            [
                "I know it when I see it in people eyes. Been doing coffee cups even before the business over the road had opened."
            ],
            [
                "We both look at each other in the eyes for a second too long."
            ],
            [
                "Well.. uh, you're pretty good."
            ],
            [
                "Eh, I don't really care that much for that. As I said, I really just wanna get out of here."
            ],
            [
                "Oh you said you wanted to play music. Right?"
            ],
            [
                "Can you play some tunes?"
            ],
            [
                "Oh well, uh... yeah. Uh, I only got instruments on my apartment. But of course I can."
            ],
            [
                "I mean... If it's alright."
            ],
            [
                "No... No... Oh, uh... it's okay."
            ],
            [
                "Uh... Maybe.. we could..."
            ],
            [
                "Uh, we can go, and I play you a new song... I've been practicing."
            ],
            [
                "For real?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah."
            ],
            [
                "Well I don't know... it's... getting a bit late."
            ],
            [
                "Oh come one, I did a coffee avoiding all security just for you, listen just one song... Take it as... a private concert."
            ],
            [
                "It's not as long as a full concert, but just... a minute or two."
            ],
            [
                "I guess [he]'s kinda right, it would only be fair, to spend a minute or two as [he] spent on making my coffee."
            ]
